'''''Anannya Nattya Goshthi''''' ({{lang-bn|অনন্যা নাট্য গোষ্ঠী}}) is a [[Bengali language|Bengali]] theatre group.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.chandpurweb.com/chandpur-local-news/2014/11/17/9000/print|title=চাঁদপুরে নাট্য কর্মীদের নিয়ে নাটক বিষয়ে ব্রিফিং {{!}} চাঁদপুর : স্থানীয় সংবাদ {{!}} চাঁদপুরওয়েব.কম|website=www.chandpurweb.com|access-date=2018-05-25}}</ref> The [[theatre]] group is located in [[Chandpur District|Chandpur]], [[Bangladesh]].[http://chandpurjomin.com/?p=25918] It was founded on 24 October 1974.<ref name="Chandpur theatre festival">{{cite news|title=Chandpur theatre festival|url=http://www.chandpur-kantho.com/index.php?ref=MjBfMTFfMTVfMTJfM18xNl8xXzI4MTUz|accessdate=20 December 2012|newspaper=chandpur-kantho.com}}</ref> [[Shahid Patwari]] is the secretary of the group.<ref name="Barna Chora Nattya Goshthi Festival">{{cite web|title=Barna Chora Nattya Goshthi Festival |url=http://www.unitednews24.com/2012/06/27/%E0%A6%9A%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%81%E0%A6%A6%E0%A6%AA%E0%A7%81%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%87-%E0%A6%87%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B6-%E0%A6%89%E0%A7%8E%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%AC-%E0%A7%A7%E0%A7%A8-%E0%A6%9C%E0%A7%81%E0%A6%B2/ |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130209033305/http://www.unitednews24.com/2012/06/27/%E0%A6%9A%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%81%E0%A6%A6%E0%A6%AA%E0%A7%81%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%87-%E0%A6%87%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B6-%E0%A6%89%E0%A7%8E%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%AC-%E0%A7%A7%E0%A7%A8-%E0%A6%9C%E0%A7%81%E0%A6%B2/ |dead-url=yes |archive-date=9 February 2013 |accessdate=20 December 2012 }}</ref>
